title: Conan O'Brien & Jeff Ross Look Back
description: Conan O’Brien and longtime executive producer Jeff Ross join writers Mike Sweeney and Jessie Gaskell to discuss Conan and Jeff's first meeting, the start of Late Night, Tom Hanks’ message to Conan, and the fate of Conan’s Ford Taurus.
author: conaf@teamcoco.com (Team Coco & Earwolf)
